data.description: Modular home on 5 acres of high and dry land. Built in 2012.  Secluded and surrounded by trees or timber to harvest if you so chose.  Fenced area for animals.  Above ground swimming pool added in 2021. Deep well with excellent water. Front entry gate.  Outdoor surround security system.  Dirt road/limerock access.
